  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p> </p>
<p><strong>Fantastic location with ski in/ski out access to the terrace just outside the ski room.</strong> It is then just a 50m ski down to the nursery slopes for beginners and the ski school meeting place. Just by this is the Funitel Peclet gondola or you can ski down to the Plein Sud chairlift, the Caron gondola or Bosimint chair within a couple of minutes on a blue piste.</p>
<p>The resort centre is just a short walk away where you can find plenty of bars, restaurants and the indoor shopping galleries.</p>
<p>Our partner ski hire shop is located within the hotel for guests staying at the property.</p>
<p> </p>]]></locationDescription>
